@state ossified
@value 3호스트 `~/.config/systemd/user/airgenome-claude.service.d/wait-for-healthy.conf` drop-in 신설. `ExecStartPost=-/bin/sh -c '\''for i in $(seq 1 60); do [ "$(docker inspect airgenome-claude --format "{{.State.Health.Status}}" 2>/dev/null)" = "healthy" ] && exit 0; sleep 1; done; exit 0'\''`. `-` prefix → best-effort (timeout 시 unit fail 안 함, Restart loop 회피). systemd 의 `restart` 자체가 healthy 까지 block — caller 가 systemctl restart 직후 `docker inspect` 해도 race 0.
